<p>Hmm. Your point is actually a good one. Why draw attention to it? Maybe because the information cordon around North Koreans has broken down enough that the regime figures the citizenry will learn about it anyway, and therefore, they should get out in front of it?</p>
<p>PS: you know, still have to get together one day. Saturday we are having Thanksgiving down here, complete with Costco turkey. Wanna come?</p>
